name: Latex (Mixed)
description:
It train on the mix image of latex (latex exp, reflect), i did obverse some unwanted images for me. (Eg, I love the models like Juli and Alex, rather than reflect ones. So, for me, I prefer to update my original model.)

Please use on https://github.com/AUTOMATIC1111/stable-diffusion-webui

Base Model

  • Chilloutmix/chilloutmix_NiPrunedFp16Fix.safetensors [59ffe2243a]

  • 512 * 768

  • Should not have watermark

Tested On

  • Chilloutmix/Chilloutmix.safetensors [a757fe8b3d]

Lion optimizer, trained on RTX4090, batch size = 8.

Additional picture source is welcomed, give me some feed back.
